						<summary>

						<p>This registers a sale of land tax-free to the temple of Paramēśvara at Tiruchcheṅgāṭṭaṅguḍi, for the maintenance of a perpetual lamp in the temple by the assembly of Marugal in Tirumarugal-nāḍu.</p>						

